{"tid":331980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺應該要block晒中國網購post個班活躍5毛份子捍衛本土?","createTime":"2017-07-22T15:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T10:59:43.000Z","uid":8129,"like":14,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ee3dd9b55aeafbe264350fca3c6f4f542fb828e","tid":331980,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"網購有好多種，要抵買，唔係剩係得大陸淘寶。唯獨連登有班愛國人士每月進貢幾千比祖國，非淘寶不買，衣、食、住、行全部都黎自淘寶，淘傢私，淘食品，淘衫褲，淘小米，淘健身器材，林林種種包羅萬有，呢班人動機明顯係抵制晒所有本土商品同外國牌子商品，但又唔返大陸住，為左係香港打工，好可能大部份係雙非，所以特別愛國需要淘寶。 經多月堪察，決定一一列出長期係中國網購post活躍份子名單，以正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一位係自稱係中國網購Post惡晒既高橋岸 疑似開分身打龍通比自己分身賺錢(分析資訊量大容後再說) 比D掌聲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/410\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/410</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://68.media.tumblr.com/7551db07eea889447e30da99f02d4ade/tumblr_othyq4Ohvx1vtg47ro1_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2F7551db07eea889447e30da99f02d4ade%2Ftumblr_othyq4Ohvx1vtg47ro1_1280.png&h=8b77685d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二位係跟左高橋岸搵食好耐既呀檸<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/656\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/656</a><br />\n<br />\n第三位係同人玩裸聊post上黎晒既中出即飛俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/m5t3v7i1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm5t3v7i1&d=HhOqQxtV6vaMmw0agYn3NNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=28f40f54\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/m5t3v7i1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/22817\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/22817</a><br />\n<br />\n第四位係長期CD-ROM MON大陸POST既黃太 block唔block都冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/964\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/964</a><br />\n<br />\n第五位係呢位<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/120850\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/120850</a><br />\n<br />\n第六位係新加人既愛國者 符碌 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/65186\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/65186</a><br />\n<br />\n第七位 呢位不得了 係唯一一位高橋岸認可既賺錢會員 疑似分身打龍通 名叫小洋蔥 (容後再說)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/78267\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/78267</a><br />\n<br />\n第八位 頂你個肺 都幾活躍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/21259\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/21259</a><br />\n<br />\n第九位 一樣的夏天 超活躍 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/21378\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/21378</a><br />\n<br />\n第十位 脆香雞翼放題 OK活躍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/2059\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/2059</a><br />\n<br />\n打住咁多先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd39f84d6dddc45b9313658fa660d85fa1753c5","tid":331980,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上個網都咁威威豬"},{"pid":"7f0b980b3322fbac5883d1f7accaa306efcef8f2","tid":331980,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小圈子post特別多痴線佬"},{"pid":"0e23f36fe948b7c7a607d5d3b372adfd1670d0c4","tid":331980,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://68.media.tumblr.com/7a09873c0c880890d531c28fa83c3d61/tumblr_oti12tBSGr1vtg47ro1_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2F7a09873c0c880890d531c28fa83c3d61%2Ftumblr_oti12tBSGr1vtg47ro1_1280.png&h=4472ed64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係之前 小洋蔥係一位長期潛伏會員 高橋岸打晒龍通 咩關係? 自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d9513baf5504ccff3139806