\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未諗到有咩用途，不過淘左先講<br />\n環保飲管 幫公司同事淘， 佢話幾好<br />\n飲管套 之前d 環保飲管無套，淘返個套俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吸色片 好用，我覺得好神奇，d淺色衫洗完真係無變色<br />\n廁所set  我覺得靚，作用不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n層架 應該好過實惠果d 我估<br />\n鐵架 買俾洗碗機同水波爐，超級fit size<br />\n箱 買黎裝頭先d印仔，不過太多印仔有d 裝唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鞋架 有d 單薄<br />\n錶帶 皮未開，金屬果條幾好<br />\n車叉 用緊，應該幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1f4f60a8e14fe9a049e080e62f898db98d508deb","tid":331980,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:31:37.000Z","msg":"歡迎知道邊個係黃犬既留低情報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1a025a8ca9a709fdc9688ccc00edd98b34b496","tid":331980,"uid":65780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:03:29.000Z","msg":"leo hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110dee8a1c572f5e1cc1018a05af6a4f0a52943c","tid":331980,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:19:12.000Z","msg":"推推先"},{"pid":"a6b29e76277beaf2ac5cca69d8e1d2527a2b0587","tid":331980,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"好惡架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9188e87fb8ed27a257530f76c98061ee0e25f09","tid":331980,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好惡架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n惡過狗 自己係咁troll 比人屌幾句就癲到走去成日去站務版投訴 當正自己係連登揸fit人"},{"pid":"c6ca00b31c42146622bb127a3bfb6a1235318e31","tid":331980,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re